quran[21{c,v,t}:
100,10,aur seenon mein jo kuch ( makhfi ) hai ussay bar aamad kar ke is ki jaanch partaal ki jaye gi ?
100,11,yaqeenan unn ka Rab uss roz unn se khoob bakhabar hoga
101,1,azeem haadsa !
101,2,kya hai woh azeem haadsa ?
101,3,tum kya jano ke woh azeem haadsa kya hai ?
101,4,woh din jab log bikhare hue parwano ki terhan
101,5,aur pahar rang barang ke dhunkay huway oon ki terhan hon ge
101,6,phir jis ke plrhe bhaari hon ge
101,7,woh dil pasand aish mein hoga
101,8,aur jis ke plrhe halkay hon ge
101,9,is ki jaye qarar gehri khayi hogi
101,10,aur tumhe kya khabar ke woh kya cheez hai ?
101,11,bharakti hui aag
102,1,tum logon ko ziyada se ziyada aur aik dosray se barh kar duniya haasil karne ki dhun ne ghaflat mein daal rakha hai
102,2,yahan taq ke ( isi fikar mein ) tum lab goar taq poanch jatay ho
102,3,"hargiz nahi, anqareeb tum ko maloom ho jaye ga"
102,4,"phir ( sun lau ke ) hargiz nahi, anqareeb tum ko maloom ho jaye ga"
102,5,"hargiz nahi, agar tum yakeeni ilm ki hesiyat se ( iss rawish ke injaam ko ) jantay hotay ( to tumhara yeh tarz amal nah hota )"
102,6,tum dozakh dekh kar raho ge
102,7,phir ( sun lau ke ) tum bilkul yaqeen ke sath ussay dekh lau ge
102,8,phir zaroor uss roz tum se inn nematon ke baray mein jawab talabi ki jaye gi
